1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,500
Most habit apps ask what you want to do.

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:06,833
This one asks who you want to become.

3
00:00:06,933 --> 00:00:09,333
It's a two-minute chat with an AI coach.

4
00:00:09,433 --> 00:00:14,033
You tell it your goal — mine was running my first 5K.

5
00:00:14,133 --> 00:00:19,133
And it writes you a real plan.

6
00:00:24,533 --> 00:00:29,333
Milestones, and a few small daily actions.

7
00:00:29,433 --> 00:00:32,133
Each day, you check off a couple of small things.

8
00:00:32,233 --> 00:00:34,067
Finish the day, and it says so.

9
00:00:34,167 --> 00:00:36,133
Your progress fills in — and never resets.

10
00:00:36,233 --> 00:00:41,233
Shape it your way: milestones, dates, how often.

11
00:00:42,433 --> 00:00:47,233
Every week, your coach checks in,

12
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:52,333
and remembers what you did.

13
00:00:53,367 --> 00:00:56,367
Then it actually coaches you —

14
00:00:56,467 --> 00:01:00,633
adjusting the plan so you don't burn out.

15
00:01:00,733 --> 00:01:05,433
Specific, personal, every single week.

16
00:01:05,533 --> 00:01:07,133
Not a tracker. Someone in your corner.

17
00:01:07,233 --> 00:01:10,233
Resolution Companion — free on the App Store.
